Time to deepen your Swiss knowledge?

Not many might know that it is illegal to keep guinea pigs individually in Switzerland-they must be housed at least in pairs. Neither is it a well-known fact that the mother of James Bond, Ian Fleming's spy creation, is Swiss.
Kai Reusser / SWI swissinfo.ch
